name: Geek Porn T-Shirt
description:
Take two of the most recognizable Video Gaming Icons, Pac-man and Space Invader, and put them on the same tee!  
 
What do you get?

Looks like perfect Geek porn fodder!

Men and Women does not have sex on their mind all the time. 

We do have other fun activities that satisfy our hormones. 

The T-Shirt is the perfect banner for men / women that are fanatics of video games that it leaves them without any form of social life. 

And quite content about it :)

Choices Choices!

name: Re-Define A Geek T-Shirts
description:
Celebrating Geekness! 

The Geek Definition T-Shirt personify our advocacy for  Anti-Bullying. 

Everyone of us has experienced some sort of bullying / misjudgement / stereotyping, irregardless of where or what's our station in life.

The definition on the shirt is funny but more than that we wanted to make people think or at the very least pause for a bit and reflect on their previous actions / ideology.

Respecting People's preference and individuality.  

Geek Shirts HQ is a brand that contribute thought provoking message through our products that we hope produce positive changes.

name: Geek Illusion Tee
description:
Take the classic geek shirts logo and turn it on its side and have it stick out of a virtual pocket.
 
There you have it virtual glasses sticking out of a virtual pocket. There you have it! My logo t shirt!
 
Why a virtual pocket?
I thought in the digital age every thing is digital.
It is not digital but just an illusion!
